Randy Spears https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Randy_Spears 0 Randy Spears (born Gregory Allan Deuschle; June 18, 1961), sometimes credited as Greg Ory, is a retired American pornographic actor and director who has appeared in numerous adult feature films. Spears is noted among porn actors for his comedic acting talent.
